WITH RULE_INFO AS
  (
SELECT
    PROJECT_NAME ,
    FOLDER_NAME,
    R.RULE_ID,
    RULE_NAME,
    CONVERT(DATE, R.RULE_CREATE_DTTM,101)        RULE_CREATED_ON,
    CONVERT(DATE, R.RULE_LAST_MODIFY_DTTM,101)  RULE_MODIFIED_ON,
    IU2.FULL_NAME                    RULE_CREATED_BY ,
    IU3.FULL_NAME                    RULE_MODIFIED_BY,
    R.RULE_TYPE,
    CASE
        WHEN IRC.EXEC_MODE ='domain'
        THEN 'Rowdiff'
        WHEN IRC.EXEC_MODE ='report'
        THEN 'Validation'
        WHEN IRC.EXEC_MODE ='scalar'
        THEN 'Checksum'
        WHEN IRC.EXEC_MODE ='recon'
        THEN 'Recon'
    ELSE 'Script'
    END RULE_OBJECT_TYPE,
    CASE
        WHEN R.RULE_STATUS = 1
        THEN 'Enabled'
        ELSE 'Disabled'
    END RULE_STATUS
FROM ICE_PROJECT P
INNER JOIN ICE_RULE_FOLDER F    ON (P.PROJECT_ID = F.PROJECT_ID)
INNER JOIN ICE_RULE R             ON (R.FOLDER_ID=F.FOLDER_ID)
LEFT JOIN ICE_RULE_CLASS IRC    ON (IRC.RULE_ID = R.RULE_ID) AND IRC.VID     = 'CompareData11'
LEFT JOIN ICE_USER IU2             ON (IU2.USER_ID=RULE_CREATED_BY_ID)
LEFT JOIN ICE_USER IU3            ON (IU3.USER_ID= RULE_LAST_MODIFY_BY_ID)
),
RULE_INSTANCE_DETAILS AS
(
 SELECT
        IRULE_INSTANCE.RULE_ID,
        IRULE_INSTANCE.RULE_INSTANCE_ID,
        CASE ISNULL(ISTATUS.STATUS_NAME ,'NoRun')
            WHEN 'Completed'
            THEN 'Success'
            WHEN 'Halted'
            THEN 'Problem'
            WHEN 'NoRun'
            THEN 'NoRun'
            WHEN 'Failure'
            THEN 'Failure'
            ELSE ISTATUS.STATUS_NAME
        END AUDIT_STATUS ,
        IRULE_CLASS_INSTANCE.STATUS_ID,
        CASE ISNUMERIC(IRULE_CLASS_INSTANCE.RULE_CLASS_RESULT)
            WHEN 1
            THEN CAST(IRULE_CLASS_INSTANCE.RULE_CLASS_RESULT AS float)
            ELSE 1
        END AUDIT_EXIT_CODE,
        CONVERT(DATE,AUDIT_START_DTTM,101) AUDIT_EXECUTION_STARTED_DT,
        AUDIT_START_DTTM AUDIT_EXECUTION_STARTED_DTTM,
        CONVERT(DATE,AUDIT_END_DTTM,101)  AUDIT_EXECUTION_COMPLETED_DT,
        AUDIT_END_DTTM AUDIT_EXECUTION_COMPLETED_DTTM,
        AUDIT_EXECUTION_MEDIUM AUDIT_EXECUTED_FROM,
        AUDIT_EXECUTED_BY_PROCESS AS CONTEXT_TYPE,
        EXECUTED_BY,
        IRULE_CLASS_INSTANCE.ROW_SRC_EXC SOURCE_ROW_COUNT,
        IRULE_CLASS_INSTANCE.ROW_TRG_EXC TARGET_ROW_COUNT,
        IRULE_CLASS_INSTANCE.RESULT_TYPE,
        CAST(MAX_ROW_COUNT AS   VARCHAR) MAX_ROW_COUNT,
        CAST(MAX_ERROR_COUNT AS VARCHAR) MAX_ERROR_COUNT,
        STORE_ERROR_ONLY STORE_ONLY_ERROR_ROWS,
        SRC_CONN SOURCE_CONNECTION_NAME,
        TRG_CONN TARGET_CONNECTION_NAME
    FROM ICE_RULE_INSTANCE IRULE_INSTANCE
    INNER JOIN ICE_RULE_CLASS_INSTANCE IRULE_CLASS_INSTANCE     ON (IRULE_INSTANCE.RULE_INSTANCE_ID = IRULE_CLASS_INSTANCE.RULE_INSTANCE_ID)
    INNER JOIN ICE_RULE_CLASS IRULE_CLASS                         ON (IRULE_CLASS.RULE_CLASS_ID = IRULE_CLASS_INSTANCE.RULE_CLASS_ID)
    LEFT JOIN  ICE_STATUS ISTATUS                                 ON (IRULE_CLASS_INSTANCE.STATUS_ID = ISTATUS.STATUS_ID)
    WHERE     IRULE_CLASS.VID LIKE '%Compare%'
  )
SELECT
    RI.PROJECT_NAME                                AS "Folder Group",
    RI.FOLDER_NAME                                AS "Folder",
    RI.RULE_ID                                    AS "Rule Id",
    RID.RULE_INSTANCE_ID                        AS "Instance Id",
    RI.RULE_NAME                                AS "Name",
    RI.RULE_OBJECT_TYPE                            AS "Rule Type",
    RI.RULE_TYPE                                AS "Criticality",
    RI.RULE_STATUS                                AS "Active",
    RI.RULE_CREATED_BY                            AS "Created By",
    RI.RULE_CREATED_ON                            AS "Create Date",
    RI.RULE_MODIFIED_BY                            AS "Updated By",
    RI.RULE_MODIFIED_ON                            AS "Update Date",
    RID.CONTEXT_TYPE                            AS "Context Type",
    SOURCE_ROW_COUNT                            AS "Source Count",
    TARGET_ROW_COUNT                            AS "Target Count",
    AUDIT_EXIT_CODE                                AS "Defect Size",
    RESULT_TYPE                                    AS "Result Type",
    AUDIT_EXECUTION_STARTED_DT                    AS "Start Date",
    AUDIT_EXECUTION_STARTED_DTTM                AS "Start Time",
    AUDIT_EXECUTION_COMPLETED_DT                AS "End Date",
    AUDIT_EXECUTION_COMPLETED_DTTM                AS "End Time",
    AUDIT_EXECUTED_FROM                            AS "Exec Src",
    CASE
        WHEN AUDIT_STATUS IS NULL
        THEN 'NoRun'
        ELSE AUDIT_STATUS
    END Result,
    SOURCE_CONNECTION_NAME                        AS "Source",
    CASE
        WHEN RULE_TYPE = 'Validation'
        THEN NULL
        ELSE TARGET_CONNECTION_NAME
    END "Target",
    CASE
        WHEN MAX_ROW_COUNT IS NULL
        OR MAX_ROW_COUNT    = -1
        THEN NULL
        ELSE MAX_ROW_COUNT
    END "Stop At Row",
    CASE
        WHEN MAX_ERROR_COUNT IS NULL
        OR MAX_ERROR_COUNT    = -1
        THEN NULL
        ELSE MAX_ERROR_COUNT
    END "Stop At Error",
    STORE_ONLY_ERROR_ROWS                        AS "Capture Err Only"
FROM RULE_INFO RI
LEFT JOIN RULE_INSTANCE_DETAILS RID ON RI.RULE_ID=RID.RULE_ID
